Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Let me design the ProgressCard component:

---

# ProgressCard Component Design for F005: Harness State Visualization

## 1. Data Requirements

Based on the harness state files and spec, the ProgressCard needs to display:

| Data Item | Source | Type |
|-----------|--------|------|
| Feature Stats | `features.json` parsed | `{ completed: number, total: number }` |
| Current Session | `progress.txt` parsed (last `SESSION:` header) | `{ name: string, date: string }` |
| Last Commit | `git log -1` via RPC/invoke | `{ hash: string, message: string }` |
| Active Feature | First feature with `passes: false` | `Feature` |

---

## 2. Props Interface

```typescript
export interface ProgressCardProps {
  /** Feature statistics */
  stats: {
    completed: number;
    total: number;
  };
  /** Current session info from progress.txt */
  session?: {
    name: string;
    date: string;
  };
  /** Last git commit info */
  lastCommit?: {
    hash: string;
    message: string;
  };
  /** Active feature (first with passes: false) */
  activeFeature?: Feature;
  /** Loading state */
  isLoading?: boolean;
  /** Error message if data fetch failed */
  error?: string | null;
  /** Callback when user clicks refresh */
  onRefresh?: () => void;
  /** Compact mode for sidebar placement */
  isCompact?: boolean;
}
```

---

## 3. Layout Wireframe (ASCII)

### Default Layout (Dashboard Placement)

```
+----------------------------------------------------------+
|  [CardHeader]                                             |
|  Progress Overview                     [RefreshButton]    |
+----------------------------------------------------------+
|  [CardBody]                                               |
|                                                           |
|  +-----------------------------------------------------+ |
|  |  [Progress Bar - 60%]                               | |
|  |  =========================================          | |
|  |  4 of 10 features completed                         | |
|  +-----------------------------------------------------+ |
|                                                           |
|  +-----------------------------------------------------+ |
|  | [DescriptionList - Horizontal]                      | |
|  |                                                     | |
|  | Session:     2026-01-04 - F011 Dev Bridge           | |
|  | Last Commit: fec6772 feat(F011): Dev Bridge...      | |
|  +-----------------------------------------------------+ |
|                                                           |
+----------------------------------------------------------+
|  [CardFooter]                                             |
|  +-----------------------------------------------------+ |
|  | [Active Feature Card - Highlighted]                 | |
|  |  [Label: F005]  [Label: medium]  [Label: ui]        | |
|  |  Harness state visualization                        | |
|  +-----------------------------------------------------+ |
+----------------------------------------------------------+
```

### Compact Layout (Sidebar Placement)

```
+--------------------------------+
|  Progress        [4/10] [60%]  |
|  ==============================|
+--------------------------------+
|  Session: 2026-01-04           |
|  Commit: fec6772               |
+--------------------------------+
|  Active: F005                  |
|  Harness state visualization   |
+--------------------------------+
```

---

## 4. PatternFly Components to Use

| Section | Components | Purpose |
|---------|-----------|---------|
| **Container** | `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardTitle`, `CardBody`, `CardFooter` | Main structure |
| **Stats** | `Progress` (with `measureLocation="top"`) | Visual progress bar |
| **Labels** | `Badge`, `Label` | Feature counts, status indicators |
| **Details** | `DescriptionList`, `DescriptionListGroup`, `DescriptionListTerm`, `DescriptionListDescription` | Session/commit info |
| **Active Feature** | Nested `Card` with `isCompact`, `Label` | Highlighted active task |
| **Icons** | `CheckCircleIcon`, `InProgressIcon`, `SyncAltIcon`, `CodeBranchIcon` | Visual indicators |
| **Actions** | `Button` (icon-only variant), `Tooltip` | Refresh button |
| **Layout** | `Flex`, `FlexItem`, `Stack`, `StackItem` | Responsive layout |
| **States** | `Spinner`, `EmptyState` | Loading/error handling |

---

## 5. Component Structure (JSX Hierarchy)

```tsx
<Card isCompact={isCompact}>
  <CardHeader
    actions={{
      actions: <RefreshButton onClick={onRefresh} />,
      hasNoOffset: true,
    }}
  >
    <CardTitle>
      <Flex alignItems={{ default: 'alignItemsCenter' }} gap={{ default: 'gapSm' }}>
        <FlexItem>
          <Icon><ChartPieIcon /></Icon>
        </FlexItem>
        <FlexItem>Progress Overview</FlexItem>
      </Flex>
    </CardTitle>
  </CardHeader>

  <CardBody>
    {isLoading ? (
      <Spinner size="lg" aria-label="Loading progress" />
    ) : error ? (
      <Alert variant="danger" title="Error loading progress" />
    ) : (
      <Stack hasGutter>
        {/* Progress Bar Section */}
        <StackItem>
          <Progress
            value={progressPercent}
            title="Features Completed"
            label={`${stats.completed}/${stats.total}`}
            measureLocation="top"
            size="lg"
            variant={progressPercent === 100 ? 'success' : undefined}
            aria-label="Feature completion progress"
          />
        </StackItem>

        {/* Session & Commit Info */}
        <StackItem>
          <DescriptionList
            isHorizontal={!isCompact}
            isCompact
            columnModifier={{ default: '1Col' }}
          >
            <DescriptionListGroup>
              <DescriptionListTerm>
                <Icon><CalendarIcon /></Icon> Session
              </DescriptionListTerm>
              <DescriptionListDescription>
                {session?.date} - {session?.name}
              </DescriptionListDescription>
            </DescriptionListGroup>

            <DescriptionListGroup>
              <DescriptionListTerm>
                <Icon><CodeBranchIcon /></Icon> Last Commit
              </DescriptionListTerm>
              <DescriptionListDescription>
                <Tooltip content={lastCommit?.message}>
                  <span>
                    <Label isCompact color="grey">{shortHash}</Label>
                    {truncatedMessage}
                  </span>
                </Tooltip>
              </DescriptionListDescription>
            </DescriptionListGroup>
          </DescriptionList>
        </StackItem>
      </Stack>
    )}
  </CardBody>

  {/* Active Feature Footer */}
  {activeFeature && (
    <CardFooter>
      <ActiveFeatureSection feature={activeFeature} />
    </CardFooter>
  )}
</Card>
```

