## 6. Responsive Behavior

| Breakpoint | Behavior |
|------------|----------|
| **Desktop (> 768px)** | Full card with horizontal DescriptionList, all info visible |
| **Tablet (576-768px)** | DescriptionList stacks vertically, commit message truncated |
| **Mobile (< 576px)** | Compact mode auto-enabled, minimal info, tap to expand |

